Kopete, The KDE Instant Messenger - ChangeLog
------------------------------------------

 HEAD
=======

o Main Application
	o Blink the metacontact status icon on the contact list whan changing the
	  status (Olivier)
	o Hide empty groups (David)
	o Show the idle time in the tool-tip (Olivier)
	o Add DCop interface to connect/disconnect an account, or load/unload a
	  plugin. Make possible to select what account to connect with the command
	  line. (Olivier)
	o URLs in the new message balloon are now clickable links that don't open
	  a chat window. (Will)
	o Allow to use customs icon for groups and metacontacts (Stephan / Olivier)
	o Allow the user to move a contact to a new metacontact (Olivier)
	o Show a link in the passive popup (i whish this could be a kdelibs item) (Olivier)
o MSN
	o New account edit page, that allow to set phone numbers, and set if we want to
	   block spam from unknown people, and show the reverse contactlist (Olivier)

Kopete 0.7.1
================

o Main Application
	o Actually _store_ the password after you type it in the dialog (the config
	  was never synced!) (Martijn)
	o fix Drag and Dorp (Olivier)
o Translator
	o Fix BabbleFish "protocol?" change (Olivier)
o MSN
	o Fix crash when filetransfer (Olivier)
	o MSNP9 implementation to be able to live after 15 oct (Olivier)


Kopete 0.7 (released 2003/08/04)
================================

o Main App
	o Multiple accounts of the same protocol are possible using the New
	  KopeteAccount architecture. (Oliver)
	o Allow custom colors for each account's icon (Duncan, Olivier)

	o Drag and Drop contacts between metacontacts (Olivier)
	o Show an icon while DNDing on the contactlist (Will, Olivier>
	o Fix up fire and forget message window, make it work for all protocols
	  (Jason)
	o Make send message keyboard shortcuts into customisable KActions (Jason)
	o Message in transit animation (Jason)
	o Message Highlighting with Notifications (Jason)
	o Add right click menu to tabs, add ability to move a tab to another window
	  (Jason)
	o Tab color highlighting on new messages, typing (Jason)
	o When a message is received, flash contact's icon to indicate a new message
	  (Oliver)
	o XML/XSL config for chatwindow theme
	o Nick completion (Jason)
	o New icon effects architecture. with overlays (Will)
	o KopeteCommandhandler for /commands. Kopete-wide support of /part, /close,
	  /clear, /exec, /help, /me (Jason)
	o New Account Password Handling, passwords are not stored in plain text
	  any more (Olivier)
	o Kopete OnlineStatus architecture (Martijn)
	o remove KopeteTransferManager (lilachaze)
	o Create KopeteViewManager, clean up KopeteMessageManager (Jason)
	o Migrate file transfers to use KIO (new standardised file transfer API in 
	  KMM)
	o General API cleanups (Everyone)
	o License headers unification and correction (Duncan)
	o Tons of bugfixes (Everyone)
	o Drag and Drop child contact beween metacontacts
o IRC Plugin
	o Total re-write of IRC, with many improvements. IRC is now integrated into
	  the Kopete chatwindow (Nick, Jason)
	o Channel / Nickname search in AddContact Wizard (Jason)
	o Add support for all /commands needed for a basic client
	o Use kopete away system
	o "Show server window" account context menu option (Michel)
	o Use KExtendedSocket for proxy and firewall support (Michel)
	o IPV6 support (Michel)
	o WHOIS support (Michel>
o OSCAR (AIM and ICQ) plugin
	o Total rewrite, ICQ now uses the newer OSCAR Protocol (Stefan)
	o More complete userinfo (Stefan, Will)
o MSN Plugin
	o Better group sync with server
	o Show the user's web profile
	o Use correct way to ping the server
	o Don't reload the contactlist from server if it is not modified
	o Correct handling of the hotmail inbox, and send mail to contact with 
	  hotmail
	o Handle MSN Plus away reasons.
	o Detect when the other party timed out and left the chat
	o Interface to allow plugins to use MSN invitations
      (all Olivier)
o Yahoo Plugin
	o First release (Matt)
o Gadu-gadu Plugin
	o Many bug fixes (Greg)
o History plugin
	o Initial Release
	o Move history/logging into its own plugin. (Olivier)
o Cryptography Plugin
	o Bug and security fixes
	o Limit the cache time for the passphrase (Olivier)
o Spell Checking Plugin
	o Initial Release
	o Enable check-as-you-type (Jason)
o Text Effect Plugin
	o Give your messages a bit of sparkle, even if you have no wit. (Olivier)
	o Initial Release (Olivier)
o Auto replace plugin
	o Initial Release
	o Perform substitutions on messages. (Roberto Pariset)



09-Febr-2003 Released Kopete 0.6
=================================

o Main App
	o Make Emoticon-mapping an external XML-file (Olivier)
	o New tabbed chatwindow (Jason)
	o Chatwindow transparency (Jason)
	o Unify away dialogs
	o Lots of bugfixing (All the team)
	o Make tabs in chatwindow detachable (Jason)
	o Make some parameters configurable (Duncan)
	o Sort contact by online status (Olivier)
	o Show number of onlines contacts in groups (Olivier)
o MSN plugin
	o Show when an user is typing a message (Olivier)
	o Outgoing file transfer (Olivier)
	o Hotmail mail notifications (Olivier, James)
	o Phone number (Olivier)
o ICQ Plugin
	o Translate between message-encodings (needed for non-latin languages) 
	  (Stefan)
	o Server contacts import
	o Receiving Files (Nick, Stefan)
o Translator Plugin
	o Option to show original messages (Olivier)
o GnuPG signing/encryption filter plugin (Oliver)
o SMS Plugin (Richard)
o Now Listening Plugin (Will)
o Web Presence Plugin (Will)



